                        <h2>Description</h2>
                        <div class="person-item-content">
                            <p>Desperately poor, Juanita has just one family member who is in no condition to help her.
                            Her legs are deformed and useless. She must crawl around the (dirt) floor of her house and
                            can not even lift herself into her wheelchair without help.</p>
                            <p>Generous neighbors have built her a chicken coop with a small door next to the floor so
                            that she can feed them while on the floor, but she does not have a good mechanism for
                            storing grain or other provisions for her chickens. She could potentially raise a few
                            more chickens if she had better provision.</p>
                            <p>She does not have an adequate toilette.</p>
                            <p>She has little ability to maintain good hygiene, no source of water at all, much less running
                            or other utilities like electricity.</p>
                            <p>She has not been to the doctor in years but suffers from pains and discomforts.</p>
                        </div>
