                            <p></p>                        
                            <p style="margin-left:2em">This section may well be the most important on the
                            website. The purpose of this space is not to honor givers; it's purpose
                            is to provide vital information to <i>potential</i> givers. Those who have
                            already helped are better placed than anyone other than the NGO worker
